item.title: Error when i want to run my server (source)
item.dc:creator: @Scape-JAVA Scape-JAVA
item.description:
@Scape-JAVA wrote:

You’re trying to the run server that has been compiled with a higher version of Java than you’re currently running, i.e;
The developer using JDK7 and then the compiler is using update 6.

If you have JDK7 change the compilers code to use your version of java, if not then install JDK7.
